0x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/robbie-williams-matty-healy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/robbie-williams-matty-healy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/robbie-williams-matty-healy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯 (Robbie Williams)</a>分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">《1975》</a>中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy)</a>的看法 – 看看下面威廉姆斯是怎么说的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/the-1975-cover-interview-2022-being-funny-in-a-foreign-language-3328010">1975 年：“我宁愿成为假装的超级恶棍，也不愿成为假装的英雄”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周末，威廉姆斯在社交媒体上写下了他对希利的看法，希利最近一直处于争议的最前沿。威廉姆斯在帖子中指出，他“哀叹摩擦、危险、个性的消亡”，同时称音乐界“无聊”，但澄清说他“并不是在攻击音乐本身”。</p><p>威廉姆斯接着表示，他理解为什么每个人都很安全：“我明白每个人都很害怕。没有人知道你会说什么会让你被取消。没有人知道你已经说过或写过什么会结束你。得罪的人太多了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3542708" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3542708" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3542708" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/robbie-williams-gareth-cattermole-1.jpg" alt="罗比·威廉姆斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/robbie-williams-gareth-cattermole-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/robbie-williams-gareth-cattermole-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/robbie-williams-gareth-cattermole-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/robbie-williams-gareth-cattermole-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/robbie-williams-gareth-cattermole-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/robbie-williams-gareth-cattermole-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3542708" class="wp-caption-text">罗比·威廉姆斯。图片来源：加雷斯·卡特莫尔/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>考虑到这一点，他称赞马蒂·希利（Matty Healy）是“我所见过的唯一一位愿意成为米色以外的有商业价值的流行/摇滚明星”。</p><p>威廉姆斯写道：“我真的很喜欢马特，他精神错乱、超级聪明、超级有才华，而且愿意让别人失望。令人心烦意乱是有原因的。原因是复杂的内心生活、叛逆的性格和无聊。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5LBW1fKTCf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.8